{"tiddlers":{"$:/plugins/dyp/text-indent-word-break/history":{"title":"$:/plugins/dyp/text-indent-word-break/history","created":"20250522121953289","modified":"20250522121959369","tags":"","type":"text/vnd.tiddlywiki","text":"v.0.0.2 2025-05-26

优化了筛选器公式，样式对影子条目也生效，示例：

```tw
<$list filter="[all[tiddlers+shadows]field:br[2]]">
```
"},"$:/plugins/dyp/text-indent-word-break/readme":{"title":"$:/plugins/dyp/text-indent-word-break/readme","created":"20250522121850706","modified":"20250522121937666","tags":"","type":"text/vnd.tiddlywiki","text":"; 根据字段内容动态应用样式-段首缩进和换行"},"$:/plugins/dyp/text-indent-word-break/usage":{"title":"$:/plugins/dyp/text-indent-word-break/usage","created":"20250522121942522","modified":"20250522121949146","tags":"","type":"text/vnd.tiddlywiki","text":"给条目添加字段则生效：

* 根据字段 `br=2` 应用换行和段首缩进两字符；
* 根据字段 `br=0` 应用换行；
* 根据字段 `in=2` 应用段首缩进两字符
"},"根据字段br=0应用换行":{"title":"根据字段br=0应用换行","code-body":"yes","created":"20240321041111881","modified":"20250522121614923","tags":"$:/tags/Stylesheet 根据字段内容动态应用样式 样式 临时编辑","text":"<$list filter="[all[tiddlers+shadows]field:br[0]]">
[data-tiddler-title^="<$view field=title/>"] .tc-tiddler-body {
  font-family: "FZYUEKZJW-H";
  text-align: justify; /* 两端对齐 */
  line-height: 1.5; /* 行高*/
  letter-spacing: 0em; /* 增加字符间距 */

/* 硬式换行 */
  word-break: normal; 
  word-wrap: break-word; 
  /* white-space: pre-wrap; 保留空白字符，包括空格、制表符和换行符。 */
  white-space:pre-line; /* 连续的空白字符合并成一个空格 */
}
</$list>
"},"根据字段br=2应用换行和段首缩进":{"title":"根据字段br=2应用换行和段首缩进","code-body":"yes","created":"20240119195219170","modified":"20250322123442086","tags":"$:/tags/Stylesheet 根据字段内容动态应用样式 html转纯文本 临时编辑","text":"<$list filter="[all[tiddlers+shadows]field:br[2]]">
[data-tiddler-title^="<$view field=title/>"] .tc-tiddler-body,
[data-tiddler-title^="<$view field=title/>"] .tc-scollpage 
{
  font-family: "FZYUEKZJW-H";
  text-align: justify; /* 两端对齐 */
  text-indent: 2em;  /* 段首缩进 */
  line-height: 1.5; /* 行高*/
  letter-spacing: 0em; /* 增加字符间距 */

/* 硬式换行 */
  word-break: normal; 
  word-wrap: break-word; 
  /* white-space: pre-wrap; 保留空白字符，包括空格、制表符和换行符。 */
  white-space:pre-line; /* 连续的空白字符合并成一个空格 */
}

[data-tiddler-title^="<$view field=title/>"] .tc-tiddler-body h3, 
[data-tiddler-title^="<$view field=title/>"] .tc-tiddler-body h4,
[data-tiddler-title^="<$view field=title/>"] .tc-tiddler-body h5, 
[data-tiddler-title^="<$view field=title/>"] .tc-tiddler-body h6,
[data-tiddler-title^="<$view field=title/>"] .tc-scollpage h3, 
[data-tiddler-title^="<$view field=title/>"] .tc-scollpage h4,
[data-tiddler-title^="<$view field=title/>"] .tc-scollpage h5, 
[data-tiddler-title^="<$view field=title/>"] .tc-scollpage h6
{
  text-indent: 0em;  /* 取消小标题段首缩进 */
  text-align: left; /* 靠左对齐 */
  font-weight: 500; /* 略微加粗 */
}

</$list>
"},"根据字段in=2段首缩进":{"title":"根据字段in=2段首缩进","code-body":"yes","created":"20240429012807086","modified":"20250522121626986","tags":"$:/tags/Stylesheet 根据字段内容动态应用样式 临时编辑","text":"<$list filter="[all[tiddlers+shadows]field:in[2]]">
[data-tiddler-title^="<$view field=title/>"] .tc-tiddler-body {
  font-family: "FZYUEKZJW-H";
  text-align: justify; /* 两端对齐 */
  text-indent: 2em;  /* 段首缩进 */
  line-height: 1.5; /* 行高*/
  letter-spacing: 0em; /* 增加字符间距 */
</$list>
"},"根据字段内容动态应用样式":{"title":"根据字段内容动态应用样式","created":"20240330061007664","modified":"20240622165405079","tags":"样式 导出","text":"<<filter-pill "[tag[根据字段内容动态应用样式]][[根据字段内容动态应用样式]]" 根据字段内容动态应用样式>>"}}}
